<i>noun</i>: 죄악 [죄ː악/줴ː악], 죄 [죄ː/줴ː] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>죄악 [죄ː악/줴ː악]</dt><br>
<dd>crime; sin</dd><br>
<dd>죄가 될 만한 나쁜 짓.</dd><br>
<dd>A wrong act that is considered a sin.</dd><br>
<dt>죄 [죄ː/줴ː]</dt><br>
<dd>guilt; sin</dd><br>
<dd>양심이나 종교적 가르침, 법에 벗어나는 잘못된 행동이나 생각.</dd><br>
<dd>A wrong act or thought that is against conscience, religious teachings or law.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>